<body>
    <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="header">
                <h4>Which community do you want to explore?</h4>
            </div>
            
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction:column;gap: 10px;">
                        <label for="" style="color: var(--purple-hue);">Plains and Mountains</label>
                        <a href="/terrestrial"><img class="img-style img-thumbnail" src="/img/land.jpg" alt="terrestrial"></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction:column;gap: 10px;">
                        <label for="" style="color: var(--purple-hue);">Seas and Oceans</label>
                        <a href="/ocean"><img class="img-style img-thumbnail" src="/img/ocean.jpg" alt="aquatic"></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction:column;gap: 10px;">
                        <label for="" style="color: var(--purple-hue);">Tropical Rainforests</label>
                        <a href="/rainforest"><img class="img-style img-thumbnail" src="/img/rainforest.jpg" alt="tropical-rainforest"></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mt-3" style="display: flex;flex-direction:column;gap: 10px;">
                        <label for="" style="color: var(--purple-hue);">Deserts</label>
                        <a href="/desert"><img class="img-style img-thumbnail" src="/img/desert.jpg" alt="xerophytic"></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            
        
        <div class="container info">
            <p><span>🐻🐼🐍🐦🐧</span># Hey Wildlife enthusiasts!<span>🐨🐯🦁🐰🐢</span></p>
            <p>Join any of the <span️>4️⃣</span> communities of "Wilderness" where you can post about campaigns,
                    charity organisations and anything you like and also would want others to
                    know about in the community page. Each community represents a particular
                    habitat related to the many species on Earth. You can pick the one
                    which has your favorite species about which you would love to know more.
                    Have fun in the wild!! <span>♥</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    
    </div>
        
